Nixpkgs Unstable Package Vinegar's Nix package resides in the Unstable repository . It can be installed system-wide with environment.systemPackages : environment.systemPackages = [ pkgs.vinegar
]; Or just for your user using home.packages via Home Manager : home.packages = [ pkgs.vinegar
]; Testing in a temporary shell can also be done using nix shell nixpkgs#vinegar
